{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The popularity baseline performs poorly because generally popular resources do not necessarily match a specific pathway or weak skill. The content-based recommender improves substantially because resource metadata overlaps with learner skill and topic needs. The hybrid model produces the strongest current ranking by adding structured pathway, skill-gap, difficulty, prerequisite, and quality signals to the content match.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The recall values are lower than precision because a top-five recommendation list cannot retrieve every resource that may be relevant in the curated label set. This is acceptable for the current prototype use case, where concise high-quality next steps are preferred over a long exhaustive list.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 4.2 Prototype Evaluation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The prototype works as a feasibility demonstration. It shows that the project can load learner and resource data, calculate skill gaps, rank resources with different models, explain recommendations, and display a staged learning path. It also provides a research view that supports model comparison.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The prototype is not yet a complete learning platform. It does not include authentication, long-term learner tracking, classrooms, payments, or formal course completion records. This is intentional because those features would distract from the recommender research question.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Planned improvements before final submission include:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab refine the dataset and relevance labels\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab add a small learner feedback study\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab strengthen the written justification for skill-map choices\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab add final report screenshots\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab prepare a clear 3-minute demonstration video\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab compare user impressions of staged recommendations against broad fixed tracks\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The demonstration video will show selecting a learner profile, viewing the staged recommendations, marking a resource as completed, resetting progress, and opening the Research View to show model metrics.\par}
